(12, 4, 1, 51, 'i-was-pregnant-at-14-now-im-a-midwife-1598296858', '\'I was pregnant at 14 now I\'m a midwife\'', 0, '<p>A mom who increased to get pregnant aged 14 states sherrrd like to utilize her experience to help other teenage parents after qualifying just like a midwife.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stephanie Master, from Whitley Bay, had boy Daniel when she was 15 years of age.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now 29 and married, mom-of-three is searching for her which you might after finishing a qualification where she labored along with her own midwives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;You aren&#39;t easily wiped off because you&#39;re a youthful mother. It changes your existence however it doesn&#39;t mean it&#39;s over,&quot; she mentioned.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Earliest boy Daniel is becoming 14 years old, the identical age his mother was when she increased to get pregnant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mrs Master has received two more children - Isaac, seven, and Freddy, six - since marriage to husband James almost 10 years ago.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>She finished a Midwifery Studies degree at Northumbria College, and helped to supply 48 healthy babies inside the three-year course.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mrs Master acquired a university place after enrolling by having an Access course when Freddy was two.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During training she labored while using community midwife who supported her during her teenage pregnancy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;I have certainly used that opportunity to inform her: &#39;Look that which you have transported out, it&#39;s because you&#39;,&quot; she told BBC Five Live.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;From the taken from that appointment just thinking the means by which she solved the problem feel am inspiring and that&#39;s things i must do, to manage to help other women because situation eventually, therefore i vowed to accomplish this.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mrs Master states she&#39;s still in touch with a couple of from the youthful mums she met while pregnant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Part of the role with any midwife is alw