 &quot;We put forth a cognizant attempt to be more forceful in the powerplay. We realized the spinners would have an effect. It was an arrangement that paid off.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;We pursued in comparable style to Friday with a wobble, yet the way Mitchell Marsh and Ashton Agar polished it off was splendid.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Previous England spinner Phil Tufnell: &quot;Britain are fit as a fiddle for the T20 World Cup. Britain get each opportunity of winning it. The white-ball game is blushing.&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'England v Australia, T20', 'T20_1599600810.jpg', '2020-09-09 01:33:30', '2021-08-17 15:17:03');
