(261, 4, 4, 60, 'tokyo-2020-olympics-must-go-ahead-at-any-cost-in-2021-japans-olympic-minister-1599601867', 'Tokyo 2020: Olympics must go ahead at any cost in 2021 - Japan\'s Olympic minister', 0, '<p>The revamped Tokyo Games must be held &quot;at any expense&quot; in 2021, says Japan&#39;s Olympic pastor Seiko Hashimoto.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Games, which had been because of start in July, were delayed for a year in March in the midst of the Covid pandemic.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On Monday, the International Olympic Committee said the occasion will proceed &quot;with or without Covid&quot;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Everybody included is cooperating to get ready and the competitors are likewise putting forth significant attempts towards one year from now,&quot; said Hashimoto on Tuesday.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;We need to hold the Games at any expense. I need to focus every one of our endeavors on measures against the Covid.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Olympic coordinators are taking a gander at more than 200 proposition on how best to manage Covid-19, including facilitating travel limitations for competitors, hostile to infection measures at the competitors&#39; town and how to adapt to onlookers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tokyo 2020 CEO Toshiro Muto has just said the Games will be &quot;streamlined&quot; and &quot;not be finished with great quality&quot;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pennant Image Reading Around the BBC - Blue&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Liverpool&#39;s 30-Year Wait: Behind the areas of their title win&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Self observer or social butterfly: Can you genuinely be either?</p>', 'Tokyo 2020, Olympics', '_114279810_tokyo2020_1599601867.jpg', '2020-09-09 01:51:07', '2021-08-14 03:43:30'),
