(263, 4, 4, 49, 'justin-and-cory-williams-the-los-angeles-brothers-creating-cycling-superstars-1599602142', 'Justin and Cory Williams: The Los Angeles brothers \'creating cycling superstars\'', 0, '<p>Sitting on the hard shoulder on a singing hot day in California, Justin Williams was broken.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through an unstable warmth dimness along the Pacific Coast Highway, he looked as passing trucks and vehicles kicked up sheets of residue, compelling it down his throat. Laying on a heap of rubble close to his bicycle, he was scarcely ready to raise a finger, not to mention get a ride.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Williams&#39; bike was in impeccable request. He hadn&#39;t tumbled off, however neither his mind nor body was functioning as it should. He&#39;d &#39;bonked&#39; - a continuance competitor&#39;s term for when the body&#39;s glucose is so low you can scarcely think straight, and your legs can no longer turn a pedal.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He was baffled, defenseless and confounded.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the long run a vehicle pulled up, and the United States&#39; future public criterium hustling champion was spared. By his auntie.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;For my first legitimate ride, my father took me 70 miles,&quot; Williams clarifies. &quot;Yet, the ride wasn&#39;t the issue - he didn&#39;t mentor me through the eating and drinking.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;My father was accustomed to encountering a ton of torment and enduring and he was determined I should have been not kidding about riding bicycles. Bikes are costly. He let me know: &#39;This is certifiably not a game and in case I will put resources into you, you should be not kidding. This is genuine cash.&#39;&quot;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Williams&#39; dad Calman was probably the best cyclist and a Pan-American Games contender. His child would proceed to turn into the USA&#39;s first dark public criterium and street hustling champion.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Justin Williams wears the stars and stripes with satisf