p and we will keep on working intimately with law implementation accomplices like the AFP to battle this detestable wrongdoing,&quot; Commander Waters said Sunday.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The man showed up in a Western Suburbs court, the Parramatta Local Court, on Saturday and was denied bail. He is next due in Sydney Central Local Court on 17 December 2020.</p>', 'Australia new, australia today, australia update, new york, usa politics, usa today', '_1603632345.jpg', '2020-10-25 17:25:45', '2021-12-19 17:23:46'),
(704, 6, 7, 186, 'fire-in-france-2020-another-big-disaster-for-france-1603638484', 'Fire in France 2020 : Another big disaster for France.', 1, '<p>A significant fire broke out on in the northern French port city of Le Havre on Saturday, the neighborhood specialists and media announced.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The fire broke out in a surrendered working in the area of Le Havre&#39;s harbor. Dull dark billows of smoke assumed control over the area close to the episode, which was noticeable from miles away.A significant fire broke out on in the northern French port city of Le Havre on Saturday, the nearby specialists and media announced.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The fire broke out in a deserted structure in the area of Le Havre&#39;s harbor. Dim dark billows of smoke assumed control over the area close to the occurrence, which was noticeable from miles away.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The specialists have begun clearing the close by territories and have requested that all occupants locate a protected sanctuary and maintain a strategic distance from the region.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>According to the nearby media reports, the fire broke out in an old Lipton stockroom.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Le Havre is one of the greatest port urban communities of the European nation France.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Starting at now, no setbacks have been accounted for. The zone has been cleared and the fire is being dealt with by the neighborhood specialists.</p>', 'france fire, france capital, french president, french products, france turkey, france fire disaster, usa today, france today', '4_1603638049.jpg', '2020-10-25 19:00:50', '2021-12-19 17:23:35'),
(705, 6, 7, 129, 'israel-and-sudan-agree-to-normalize-ties-with-us-help-1603718582', 'Israel andSudan Agree to Normalize Ties With U.S. Help', 0, '<p>Israel and Sudan on Friday consented to standardize relations in an arrangement facilitated with the assistance of the United States, making Sudan the third Arab nation to put aside threats with Israel in the previous two months.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>U.S. President Donald Trump, looking for re-appointment on November 3, fixed the arrangement in a call on Friday with Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu and Sudanese Prime Minister Abdalla Hamdok and Transitional Council Head Abdel Fattah al-Burhan, senior U.S. authorities said.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trump likewise reported that assignments between the two nations will before long meet so as to examine participation in an assortment of fields, among them agribusiness and exchange, and included that the &quot;skies of Sudan are available to Israel today,&quot; taking into consideration immediate and more limited trips among Israel and Africa and South America.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a major aspect of the understanding, Trump found a way to eliminate Sudan from a U.S. government rundown of nations advancing illegal intimidation. A senior U.S. official said Trump marked an archive on Air Force One on Thursday night to advise Congress of his goal to eliminate Sudan from the rundown.</p>', 'Israel and sudan, israel today, israel and use, israel trump, trump, today, sudan update, usa update, usa daily, corona update, covid-189', 'israeel_1603718581.jpg', '2020-10-26 17:23:02', '2021-12-19 17:25:24'),
(706, 6, 6, 185, 'caged-bull-bitcoin-crosses-the-13k-breakout-mark-1603720799', '( Caged Bull ) Bitcoin Crosses The $13K \'Breakout\' Mark', 1, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bitcoin (BTC) crossed the $13,000 blemish on Saturday, the first run through since Jan. 2018, as indicated by CoinMarketCap information.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What Happened: The zenith digital money has risen 14.85% in the course of the most recent seven days as of press time, CMC information recommends.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There was a concise upsurge in Bitcoin costs in late June and early July 2019, when the digital currency exchanged over the $13,000 level, CoinDesk detailed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The digital money market flooded throughout the end of the week, yet the market saw a remedy late Sunday and early Monday. By and by, BTC kept on stepping over the mental $13,000 mark.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bitcoin exchanged at $13,101.56, lower by 1.33% at press time. Ethereum (ETH), the second-biggest digital money by market valuation, was down 2.18% at $406.57. Among other significant cryptographic forms of money, (XRP) was down about 0.3% at $0.26. Bitcoin hard fork Bitcoin Cash (BCH) was down 1.47% at $269.96.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A Bloomberg Intelligence report in July stuck $13,000 as a breakout focus for Bitcoin, naming it a &quot;confined bull.&quot;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>New Traders Swear By Benzinga Options&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We filter through this unpredictable market for steady exchanges so you don&#39;t need to. Get Benzinga Options: Starter Edition to follow Benzinga&#39;s high-conviction choices exchanges. Snap here to buy in.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why It Matters: The world&#39;s pinnacle cryptographic money hitting the key benchmark followed a whirlwind throughout the most recent week.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PayPal Holdings Inc&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PYPL 0.32%&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>reported it would permit its clients to purchase, sell, and hold cryptographic forms of money including Bitcoin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>That declaration prompted a feeling of &quot;vindication&quot; in the Bitcoin people group, with some like Social Capital CEO Chamath Palihapitiya recommending the move could fuel further appropriation by banks.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This month, Jack Dorsey-drove Square Inc&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SQ 0.75%&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>said it was putting $50 million in Bitcoin.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Barry Silbert, CEO of Grayscale, said that the speculation firm included $300 million out of a solitary day last Thursday to its advantages under administration.</p>', 'bitcoin, bitcoin update, bitcoin rate, usa bitcoin, canada bitcoin, australia bitcoin, usa today, usa news, bitcoin news', 'bit_1603720799.jpg', '2020-10-26 17:59:59', '2021-12-19 17:23:21'),
(707, 6, 15, 271, 'more-than-15-million-people-were-in-khadim-hussain-rizvi-funeral-chief-tlp-1606132216', 'More than 15 Million people were in Khadim Hussain Rizvi Funeral, Chief TLP', 1, '<p>Millions of mourners, followers and fans Saturday attended the funeral of the 54-year-old Tehreek-i-Labbaik Pakistan chief and firebrand orator, Allama Khadim Hussain Rizvi, at Lahore&rsquo;s historic Minar-i-Pakistan, undoubtedly making it one of the biggest events of its kind recorded in this Metropolis during the last 100 years.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://news-zilla.com/uploads/ckeditor/kk_1606121006.jpg\" style=\"height:50%; width:100%\" /><br />\r\nIt was sea of people which filled the vast spaces at the Greater Iqbal Park,&nbsp;On Saturday, too, the crowd, overflowed on to various tributaries of the Circular Road and Ravi Road that skirt the Iqbal Park on the north-westerern side of the Badshahi Mosque. Some witnesses said that the number of people who had collected at the funeral prayers ran into many Millions.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://news-zilla.com/uploads/ckeditor/k_1606121209.jpeg\" style=\"height:50%; margin:10px; width:100%\" /><br />\r\nBy the time it reached the funeral place some four hours behind schedule, the procession had grown into around three kilometers in length, with a multitude of people waiting in and around Iqbal Park.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe crowd peacefully dispersed after the funeral.</p>', 'khadim rizvi funeral, world biggest janaza, people in rizvi funeral, biggest funeral, khadim rizvi janaza, rizvi grave, biggest funeral khadim rizvi, tlp chief funeral, mumtaz qadri funeral, hajj ijtema, world record muslim', 'rizvi_1606121296.jpg', '2020-11-23 13:48:17', '2021-12-19 17:23:09');
